física","guid":"mJpk1vdN9556sMpOktA8eg","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"0","text":"- Prevalencia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"- Variable según definición y población de estudio","guid":"oJmVxksWcBTsSr5fGIabvw","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"- Asociada con:","guid":"6efbYO_r0CVIRF9Pb2jvnQ","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"- ↓ Función renal","guid":"0uy3Kbd8JdLs3RmPI4KbIg","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"- ↑ Inflamación","guid":"uWUdOYjWJzx_8XW7-423qw","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"- Desgaste\\Nproteico-energético","guid":"O47ueMeEFk6tk0cOeulQlw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"- Factores\\Ncontribuyentes:","guid":"IGhzg9q5BOSgZCEzWZPZBw","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"- Inactividad física","guid":"5Mz68DrscxWvFI5GDrsYOg","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"- Alteraciones nutricionales","guid":"dC_YvaN3lLPBAOBAbbKsyA","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"- Comorbilidades (ej. diabetes)","guid":"4mXPdoLFzgMIcJUC5sOvmg","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"- Implicaciones\\Npara Manejo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"- Identificación temprana y seguimiento de pacientes con CKD","guid":"cjiQDthWneJsvChmDDSejQ","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"- Implementación de estrategias preventivas y terapéuticas","guid":"E0ozDfLHnDqO6nptr05Qfg","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"→ Ejercicio","guid":"oupHWYUgMTdUXkEmagdu4Q","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"→ Intervenciones\\Nnutricionales","guid":"BmARr6MiedEMwDkjT-9e9g","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"→ Corrección de desbalances\\Nhormonales y metabólicos","guid":"F6Z0Pv1IfGk2oFjyNuJO5w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"0","text":"Factores de Riesgo de Sarcopenia\\NUremica en CKD y ESKD:","guid":"Z53CYJQyDaGvsmv3R2842A","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"- Envejecimiento: ↑ Prevalencia de CKD +\\Naceleración de la pérdida muscular normal","guid":"ZtCqAESE9M_IP2IZSbZMrQ","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"- Inflamación Crónica: ↓ Masa y función muscular\\N+ ↑ Pérdida de peso + Debilidad muscular","guid":"gpflzDHzhekrV9yWSdFgRQ","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"- Citocinas inflamatorias + Estrés oxidativo\\N+ Destrucción mediada por inactividad de la homeostasis proteica = Destrucción catabólica de proteínas","guid":"5gU8a82cR-S-pqSRGdTxcg","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"- Estado de Inflamación: ↑ MIS + ↑ CRP, IL-6,\\Nβ2-microglobulina = asociado a sarcopenia","guid":"qhJMyJ94lQCcv36YNeO4KA","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"32","text":"- Malnutrición: ↓ Peso/BMI, ↓ Albumina/prealbumina,\\N↑ MIS, pérdida de nutrientes por diálisis","guid":"1BA2HyopsjNhbaqM5ZCTOQ","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"32","text":"- Cambios Uremicos: Acidosis metabólica + Metabolitos uremicos\\Nderivados del intestino + Factores relacionados con la diálisis","guid":"WXjUU8ZBLbanzch95rekRQ","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"32","text":"- Cambios Mecánicos: Inactividad + Artropatía +\\NIngresos hospitalarios recurrentes","guid":"fvEoaSLGsaMujBFncv26SA","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"32","text":"- Cambios Inmunológicos y del Sistema\\NRenina-Angiotensina: ↑ Angiotensina II","guid":"5Lo4T4mf7efEMY3ZxZqQVw","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"32","text":"- Cambios Hormonales: ↓ Hormona de crecimiento,\\NPTH, insulina, IGF-I, hormonas sexuales","guid":"dg8BHzRDDS-C0NYIj1ZUpQ","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"32","text":"- Condiciones Comórbidas: Diabetes, enfermedades\\Ncardiovasculares, infecciones, deficiencia de vitamina D","guid":"ll6we8v1bCCPQm3sPDl9TQ","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"32","text":"- Circulación Muscular: ↓ Perfusión,\\Nanemia renal, ↓ Capilares","guid":"NHnqh-Niq_DljbUHWJoucQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"32","text":"- Cambios Mentales: Depresión,\\Ndeterioro cognitivo leve","guid":"c7a0G5Kur1E6_JcM_pEU6w","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"32","text":"- Disfunción mitocondrial\\N+ Estrés Oxidativo","guid":"9bl9u_koCTbi6JzE-0Z1PQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"32","text":"- Cambios en el Balance Proteico Muscular: ↓ Síntesis\\Nde proteínas musculares + ↑ Proteólisis muscular","guid":"bm2IBuiGukHZ_k_C7TQ8cg","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"0","text":"Microbioma Intestinal y\\NMetabolitos Uremicos en CKD:","guid":"ItY9f3-W36R7RPUiZvcpDQ","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"1. Microbioma\\NIntestinal en CKD:","guid":"blwMKUtvMX-mLJjQAHMtHg","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"- ↑ Ingreso de urea y toxinas → Cambios en el microbioma → Crecimiento de patógenos","guid":"XAM8ETfhxhio79F2fPtATQ","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"- ↓ Bacterias benéficas (p. ej., Lactobacillus, Bifidobacterium) → ↓ Ácidos grasos de cadena corta","guid":"b0ek75I-6THhotX_iZUlMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"2. Producción de\\NMetabolitos Uremicos:","guid":"422Pvvpi4A-OKLPep00BrQ","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"- ↑ Bacterias productoras de toxinas (IS, PCS, TMAO) → Efectos nocivos en músculos","guid":"HVVRmAnf8PBYIelcqgOAnA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"- ↑ Bacterias con triptofanasa y ureasa → ↑ Producción de toxinas urémicas (sulfato de\\Nindoxilo [IS], sulfato de p-cresilo [PCS], óxido de trimetilamina-N [TMAO])","guid":"qCyhHXLozw4B2WZC7ZyOug","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"47","text":"3. Efectos en Músculos\\NEsqueléticos:","guid":"Y1px-Uc-LsLt5ajG4gPo4g","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"- ↑ Metabolitos urémicos derivados del intestino + ↑ Permeabilidad epitelial → Acumulación\\Nde metabolitos urémicos en el músculo → ↓ Masa muscular o ↑ Contenido lipídico","guid":"qvwIjtptYzlFJ0tmHkGiOA","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"- Eje Riñón-Intestino-Músculo:","guid":"QEdo9IgKdPFNQxo1VD7gxQ","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"- Disfunción renal → Disbiosis intestinal → ↑ Metabolitos urémicos circulantes\\N→ ↓ Masa muscular, alteración de la composición muscular y ↓ Función física","guid":"KVhjdJIrBcsYpmMf9GDPSw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"47","text":"4. Mecanismos\\NMoleculares:","guid":"EswLzHebrnOH7Wxy4JD6eA","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"- Metabolitos (p. ej., IS) entran a células musculares → Activación de NADPH oxidasa → ↑ ROS\\N→ Inflamación y expresión de miostatina y atrogin-1 → Degradación muscular","guid":"4zdx0hnXy_A0xS-8NxuHqg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"- IS afecta mitocondrias → Disfunción y ↓ Producción de ATP\\N→ Pérdida de masa muscular","guid":"s8PtfhAb_NudLIvyvgZpKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"47","text":"5. Estrategias de\\NIntervención:","guid":"rh_6rHaB7s60d5agOTimkQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"- Suplementos bióticos para modificar el microbioma","guid":"c6tpUYhlnFtRpEebu0sdqQ","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"- Adsorbentes orales para reducir metabolitos\\Nurémicos y mejorar la barrera intestinal","guid":"xECdnEeseL4ADjFcYE0sXw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"0","text":"Estrategias para Prevenir y\\NTratar la Sarcopenia:","guid":"-DNOlimxtoy1A2hesfUM8g","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"1. Ejercicio → Aeróbico + Resistencia","guid":"KVEnMoBta0WKcbRhHzL8Ig","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"→ Mejoran masa y función muscular","guid":"z_sVsAoaRYq8RBCVwGULOQ","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"→ Previenen deterioro relacionado con CKD","guid":"H4bMn5g6xsrDw3r-ZFWkUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"2. Intervenciones Nutricionales → Suplementos orales\\N+ Nutrición parenteral intradialítica","guid":"SfISxxGzRK6wN8FGOPIODw","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"- Estimulantes del apetito\\N(p. ej., Megestrol)","guid":"uCm8Zayu9m7hVIiEUPWzyA","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"64","text":"3. Hormonas Anabólicas → Esteroides\\Nanabólicos, hormonas de crecimiento","guid":"lGlk9NncSqTOSsHJGIWBSw","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"- Hormona de crecimiento recombinante","guid":"irWejjrvAn6mNrRXVc7g9w","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"→ Mejoran masa y fuerza muscular","guid":"hH_wM1-v0GIJEsmiIqhjOw","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"64","text":"4. Corrección → Acidosis metabólica,\\Nestado de vitamina D","guid":"zZsCgwE7SWsk4F4-HU0dbQ","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"→ Contribuyen a la mejora de la\\Nfunción y masa muscular","guid":"MpsH3CzLU5MZ2XiEq1ItlQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"64","text":"5. Bioticos → Mejora microbioma\\Nintestinal, reduce toxinas uremicas","guid":"mgp63WEr6U3PbpoRs-QEoA","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"- Suplementos bióticos para mejorar composición del microbioma","guid":"FipdI6qGWeSXhb8uMtu-PA","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"- Adsorbentes orales\\N(p. ej., AST-120)","guid":"_YwmKzvqHLabPpt1YP6TFQ","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"→ Reducen toxinas urémicas,\\Nmejoran función muscular","guid":"3r1qBrTx3nF08UqqpHaFTA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"64","text":"6. Adsorbentes Orales → Restauran composición\\Nmicrobioma intestinal, integridad pared intestinal","guid":"Okr8fkr0eCL3oyGxw5LBfw","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"- Bimagrumab: anticuerpo monoclonal,\\Nbloquea receptor de activina tipo-2B","guid":"go6chemk5VDvMM6F7_AqjA","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"- Sarconeos (BIO101): esteroide\\Nvegetal, actúa sobre receptor MAS","guid":"Jl-hV3g_uMqNshavq-J6iA","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"- Efectos:","guid":"3IZ2y7nnyqjfvPIzKZadlQ","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"→ Pérdida de grasa,\\Nganancia de masa magra","guid":"tEmiElHGqgQrmvyFb92hfA","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"→ Mejoras metabólicas en pacientes\\Ncon diabetes y obesidad","guid":"ecQgkTSq8T_RTDTtFJADbQ","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"→ Mejoras significativas en\\Npruebas de función física","guid":"3KHEClnEmlXzIoqdgc1C2w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"64","text":"7. Abordaje\\NMultifacético:","guid":"tuImombDIB776i1SWGig3Q","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"- Necesario para reducir carga de\\Nsarcopenia en pacientes con CKD","guid":"hzWyKNO5mLQl2dQxyIS8tA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"0","text":"Acetato de Megestrol\\Nen Hemodiálisis:","guid":"RVNSKtvlDk5f6rOUtZMVmA","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"- Población: Pacientes 40-80 años, sin función renal residual","guid":"QTrkNbnfS1l6Z1jXm-kFFQ","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"- Tratamiento: 160 mg/día, 2-12 meses","guid":"cZvwOCLpq55PSNDaaBwJgA","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"88","text":"- Resultados:","guid":"K3SfnmB3GUTzVbSb6pDLNA","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"- ↑ Peso: 2-9 kg","guid":"N2_98-hgEPwEo_bLwwKaPA","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"- ↑ Tasa catabólica de proteínas","guid":"c38GzqiODg4YxrSoP8ITPQ","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"- ↑ Concentración de [sustancia no especificada]","guid":"MqYL3vk_CNwqBQw3B9MR2g","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"88","text":"- Mecanismo:","guid":"7N6z_u3k7_oV2CidprZ0VA","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"- Estimulante del apetito","guid":"CdJSGneTNh-cRPc5VkTJfQ","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"- Contribuye a la ganancia de peso y\\Nmejora del estado nutricional","guid":"aFTmmrJQxPiSdULU7w8v1w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"98","parent":"0","text":"Vitamina D en\\NCKD y HD:","guid":"Uj5F13hvC8hy80TwDU5gjg","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"1. Pacientes CKD (etapas 3 a 4)\\Ny PD con deficiencia:","guid":"5wKy5BtSePtV-v5m_MVvRw","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"- Tratamiento con vitamina D →\\NSuficiencia de vitamina D","guid":"iMxWL4tUSVSjjN1kws1GzQ","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"- Mejoras en:","guid":"Vo-GtJ8_beMh3FMuyErKLw","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"- Función física (timed up and go,\\Nvelocidad de marcha, etc.)","guid":"0gPhWxUidkZZB0L3UzzBUA","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"- Fuerza isométrica","guid":"OgrrFVLuZkqrCcZCGmZDaA","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"- Masa muscular en\\Npacientes HD masculinos","guid":"C-S4WX43Rvg6FRCCYMRKng","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"98","text":"2. Suplementación de Colecalciferol\\N(50,000 unidades/semana):","guid":"LxyaU50ZPttjduI-TtV0hA","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"- Objetivo: Concentración de\\N25(OH)D >80 nmol/L","guid":"7rNs0d8MSngcVov0zRKOGg","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"- En pacientes HD con\\N25(OH)D inicial <50 nmol/L:","guid":"2Ll2_mehxeJMBH_Vyd0sXw","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"- Sin efecto en la fuerza\\Nmuscular o síntomas","guid":"zM-6kq0csIqY0yDBeo-Yhg","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"98","text":"3. Tratamiento de 8 semanas + 4\\Nmeses mensuales en HD:","guid":"lhwLzIYBdhBAKtrTujboQw","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"- Con concentración\\N25(OH)D <60 nmol/L:","guid":"_LjaDyHWV7sdk0dqetMlrQ","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"- Aumento de niveles\\N25(OH)D y 125(OH)2D","guid":"tTXNLOWGPHedc1xeNRgeJA","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"- Sin aumento en niveles\\Nde calcio o fósforo","guid":"eYAmWAKN10J8eYTzm_ySGg","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"109","text":"- Sin cambio en fuerza muscular,\\Ncapacidad funcional o QoL","guid":"nw8TrbWRoBZISu-JZv6jig","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"0","text":"Terapias Hormonales para\\NSarcopenia Uremica:","guid":"qplyx04EmxgNF4xspKoa5Q","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"1. Nandrolona\\N(Decanoato):","guid":"kPNf0NGLgcS79XgFh5X_fQ","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"- Andrógeno y\\Nesteroide anabólico","guid":"cEkFbsQhMJwLfb9C0qqxVg","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"- Administración IM o SC en\\Npacientes HD durante 6 meses","guid":"4ZNQsqeveQsraaSaeIEZVg","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"115","text":"- Resultados:","guid":"lKrOn_9g79KpNdSBHC1vEQ","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"→ ↑ Masa\\Ncorporal\\Nmagra","guid":"NGRHs4xm1eHO29HjcS9tfQ","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"→ Mejora capacidad\\Nfuncional (pruebas de\\Ncaminar y subir escaleras)","guid":"-WvWmD4oBU0vhgIoTZnI6w","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"118","text":"→ ↑ Masa magra apendicular de\\Nmanera dosis-responsiva","guid":"Kxfe6jCAAmrnmF9iRzIZSQ","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"118","text":"→ Con entrenamiento de resistencia\\Nintradialítico: ↑ área transversal del\\Nmúsculo cuádriceps","guid":"2VgzCw2h6998-Ow6j57SMw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"123","parent":"114","text":"2. Oximetolona:","guid":"LmJ8My4gsuQLTV5dREZVew","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"- Andrógeno y\\Nesteroide anabólico\\Noral","guid":"E2snFwn0lnGABNMG05Ib5w","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"- Mayor efecto anabólico y\\Nmenor actividad androgénica\\Nque la testosterona","guid":"YdznhhWXQJCz8X-6doCdRg","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"123","text":"- Resultados en\\Npacientes HD:","guid":"jkqoW7U16ZukHy9Vsrg68Q","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"→ ↑ Masa libre de grasa, fuerza\\Nde agarre y puntuaciones de\\Nfuncionamiento físico","guid":"Y3g7YJ-AI5yBL5QUNjIEqg","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"→ ↑ Expresión de ARNm para cadena pesada de\\Nmiosina y factores de crecimiento similares a la\\Ninsulina (IGF)-I/II en músculos","guid":"aW8fbL_tDVAr1PbOUxlNjA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"114","text":"3. Hormona de\\NCrecimiento (GH):","guid":"sp7R2QH6ADspbhZB2jKtFA","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"- Efecto: ↑ Masa muscular, ↓ Grasa corporal","guid":"SI7SZPDdr2zrz2xMlWg-0A","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"- Vía: Inyección IM o SC","guid":"oPOehwzQ41_H4TXm6tSMXg","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"129","text":"- Duración: 6 meses en pacientes HD","guid":"czaQvvqHRX9udtYgRNIy2A","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"129","text":"- Nota: Requiere monitoreo de IGF-1","guid":"PmcKFWEtpqU8mb6cFAoA1Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"114","text":"4. Agonistas de la\\NHormona del Crecimiento:","guid":"-ciGnEHWekTtCIYWhh5DEA","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"- Ejemplos: CJC-1295","guid":"pW-jHWlG-NdJfKalG3H5yw","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"- Efecto: Estimula producción de GH","guid":"ASxariRtFnUBs9m9kM_dDA","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"- Vía: Inyección SC","guid":"da4-k9NI5ZD-_FMbBk5njw","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"114","text":"5. Péptidos de IGF-1:","guid":"-soDmMMgEEbL2i-75liDgA","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"- Ejemplos: Mecasermin\\N(Increlex)","guid":"pDSLawSCem4ztie80caYYw","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"- Efecto: Acción similar a IGF-1, ↑ Masa muscular","guid":"IvpqVuCgr7Lzal8mmZ9HCQ","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"- Vía: Inyección SC","guid":"sDO1DAtYIvzXrRQMZylXzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"114","text":"6. Moduladores Selectivos del\\NReceptor Androgénico (SARMs):","guid":"YPt1FVPJ9WDjWDTxUzIURg","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"- Ejemplos: Ostarine","guid":"7g3yvmEYzZuJU7QRW-HeXw","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"- Efecto: ↑ Masa muscular, sin\\Nefectos secundarios de EA","guid":"eRXLXOAeFN4gjH8KQOWYuA","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"- Vía: Oral","guid":"SG5lUBX8sWNCPc9U60sG2Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"146","parent":"114","text":"7. Hormonas\\NSexuales:","guid":"ZiMj66wA1g7X_HbDrMap_w","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"- Testosterona (Hombres): Gel, parches, inyecciones","guid":"OB0Xf5N_RI4-GJ4SHGr5nw","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"- Estrógenos (Mujeres): Terapia de reemplazo hormon