ón\\Nmitocondrial, supresión de\\Nexpresión atrogin-1/myostatina","guid":"Q4OOjVvUQmD7JXgBnq72bg","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"185","text":"3. Mejora de Función\\NFísica en Humanos:","guid":"ArIVt7hFnUbIMGW_I0u3mw","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"- RCT en Humanos: ↑ Velocidad de\\Nmarcha en 1 año con AST-120","guid":"Xdsnu99NBz0F_0flMK4rDA","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"- Mejoras en dolor corporal, vitalidad,\\Nproblemas/síntomas cognitivos","guid":"290SU4MlFZkY1YJRRhVs_g","children":[]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"185","text":"4. Restauración de Microbioma\\Ny Pared Intestinal:","guid":"TC1ZwfMMESZFcQTqGo5EGg","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"- Restauración parcial de proteínas de\\Nunión epitelial → ↓ Endotoxinas, estrés\\Noxidativo, inflamación","guid":"UhN2sEZ-qw-j6ghEOp5hXg","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"185","text":"5. Mejora de Fisiología\\NMuscular Esquelética:","guid":"5WUHcK4hMBL7r7r5ez9Xmg","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"- Incremento de peso muscular\\Nesquelético en ratones CKD","guid":"0pRDx1ahpDHQ1F0-GpQNCw","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"- ↑ Expresión renal de Klotho,\\Nrelacionada con fisiología muscular","guid":"28ZD6zSVE71LSQSjjlDU5w","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":199,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Geriatría","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Geriatría","filename":"Sarcopenia uremica-2024-1","id":"map_1007","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Sarcopenia uremica-2024-1"}